  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんかもう俺
ちょっと楽しくなってきちゃったよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm kinda starting to actually have fun with this.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>俺さまも、ロイドくんと一緒だから
けっこう楽しんでるよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I too am having a delightful time,
since I'm here with you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>まぁでも、そろそろキメたいよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But well, I think it's time we made a decision.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>目指せ！　主人公！
目指せモテモテな俺さま！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Time to get in gear! To be the protagonist!
Time to get in gear for me to be hella popular!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>さて、初心を思い出したとこで
気合い入れていくよー！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Alrighty, now that I actually remembered what I was originally doing here, let's get that fighting spirit going!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
